      <title>意大利的梅洛尼（Meloni）在伦敦安全峰会之前与特朗普进行了交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/italy-s-meloni-spoke-with-trump-ahead-of-london-security-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治·梅洛尼（Giorgia Meloni）周六晚与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）通过电话交谈，在欧洲安全峰会之前，她将与乌克兰的领导人会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/italy-s-meloni-spoke-with-trump-ahead-of-london-security-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 04:42:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/most-thais-not-confident-in-paetongtarn-s-government-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一项民意测验，大多数泰国人对总理佩顿顿·辛瓦特拉（Paetongtarn Shinawatra）的政府没有信心，因为它在过去六个月中未能恢复全国苦苦挣扎的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/most-thais-not-confident-in-paetongtarn-s-government-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 04:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦莉（Milei</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/milei-to-seek-congress-support-for-imf-deal-in-coming-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米利（Javier Milei）周六晚宣布，他将为他的政府与国际货币基金会进行谈判的新计划寻求国会支持，这是迄今为止最具体的迹象，即谈判将在最后阶段前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/milei-to-seek-congress-support-for-imf-deal-in-coming-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 02:48:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普解雇举报机构负责人裁定非法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/trump-firing-of-whistleblower-agency-head-unlawful-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官裁定，保护政府举报者的一名独立美国机构的负责人上个月被唐纳德·特朗普总统非法开除，即使白宫的目标是将案件置于最高法院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/trump-firing-of-whistleblower-agency-head-unlawful-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 01:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
