    <item>
      <title>墨西哥的Sheinbaum说，今年可能会削减CFE单位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-cfe-units-likely-to-be-cut-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统克劳迪娅·辛巴姆（Claudia Sheinbaum）周六表示，墨西哥可能会在今年取消该州电力公司的子公司，以垂直整合该公用事业公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-cfe-units-likely-to-be-cut-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 23:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列接受我们提出加沙休战的建议，敦促哈马斯加入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-accepts-us-proposal-for-ramadan-truce-pm-s-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）的办公室宣布，以色列接受了美国的新加沙停火提案，在暂停哈马斯敌对行动的数小时之前，以色列接受了新的停火提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-accepts-us-proposal-for-ramadan-truce-pm-s-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 22:22:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙总理在反对派的帮助下避免了危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/portugal-prime-minister-says-political-crisis-should-be-avoided</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·黑山（Luis Montenegro）在试图结束对与一家家族企业有关的潜在利益冲突的猜测之后，从反对派社会主义者那里得到了避免政治危机的帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/portugal-prime-minister-says-political-crisis-should-be-avoided</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 20:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列“准备”捍卫大马士革附近的叙利亚德鲁兹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-poised-to-defend-druze-near-damascus-from-regime-forces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长说，大马士革南部的城镇贾拉马纳（Jaramana）的少数民族德鲁兹（Druze）受到新叙利亚政权的攻击，他命令以色列部队有望在必要时帮助保护他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-poised-to-defend-druze-near-damascus-from-regime-forces</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 18:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
